Current figures suggest that 1 in 6 women and 1 in 33 men will become a victim of sexual assault in his or her lifetime. As a victim of sexual assault myself, I'm driven to take action. RAINN (Rape, Abuse, and Incest Network) has helped me realize that there's something I can do - something we can all do, to actually affect change and not just talk about it.

Ending sexual violence is a cause worth fighting for, and RAINN is an organization worth supporting. RAINN has helped more than 2 million survivors through the National Sexual Assault Hotline (800.656.HOPE and online.rainn.org) and they work every day to shine light on the issue, and to ensure justice for survivors.

Please support me today and together, we can make a difference. 92¢ of every dollar will go directly to RAINN's programs to help survivors, educate the public and improve sexual assault laws and policies. Absolutely NONE of the proceeds go to me! When you donate, you are donating directly to RAINN.
